  "2126810": {
    "name": "Memory's Reach",
    "steam_appid": 2126810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索迷宫般的巨型结构，解决令人费解的谜题，并掌握神奇的外星科技，展开一场充满谜团的银河探险。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >失落星球上的古代宝藏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅凭古老的星图和可疑的传闻，踏上前往失落已久的维里沙尔星球的旅程。探索一个由高耸的巨型结构和荒芜的废墟组成的世界——一个在巨大灾难中被毁灭的文明。其纪念碑如今被蒸腾的丛林吞噬，埋藏在崩塌的矿井中，或在缓慢衰败的轨道上逐渐崩塌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片世界某个角落，隐藏着玛丽古文明的古代宝藏，它被封印了无数个世纪，以保护它免受大灾难的侵袭。探索维里沙尔，寻找宝藏——但要小心，这颗行星表面之下还潜伏着其他危险的秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/234e0f2945e97cc8dd1af4df72691415.poster.avif?t=1755126652\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/234e0f2945e97cc8dd1af4df72691415.webm?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/234e0f2945e97cc8dd1af4df72691415.mp4?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索强大新能力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上冒险之旅，探索宁静的漂浮城市、庞大的地下结构和危险的轨道空间站。随着你解决谜题并获得强大新能力，世界将逐步展开。利用你的能力打开通往此前无法进入区域的通道，克服曾经无法逾越的障碍，揭开隐藏的秘密，并解决全新类型的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/703d26d76f3fd91873d8509fa80079a0.poster.avif?t=1755126652\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/703d26d76f3fd91873d8509fa80079a0.webm?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/703d26d76f3fd91873d8509fa80079a0.mp4?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >破解神秘谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你解决具有挑战性的全息谜题并掌控强大的外星科技，庞大的机械装置开始苏醒。移动的墙壁、能量光束及其他奇异机制构成庞大且相互连接的谜题房间——利用所有可用工具，破解这些复杂谜题，考验你的逻辑思维与空间推理能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/e4e0fe25d3033159d0b120a287016873.poster.avif?t=1755126652\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/e4e0fe25d3033159d0b120a287016873.webm?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/e4e0fe25d3033159d0b120a287016873.mp4?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开宇宙遗产</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亿万年前，一场毁灭性的灾难终结了一个高度发达的文明。数百年后，关于古代宝藏的传闻将你——一位星际宝藏猎人——吸引至这片荒凉的世界。扫描环境以获取传说，寻找隐藏的遗物，并拼凑散落的数据碎片，揭开一个灭绝民族的惨痛历史，并揭示一个注定灭亡的文明的遗产！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/e32256a2f15b1593057b0900820c3e61.poster.avif?t=1755126652\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/e32256a2f15b1593057b0900820c3e61.webm?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126810/extras/e32256a2f15b1593057b0900820c3e61.mp4?t=1755126652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多内容即将推出！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《记忆的触角》是独立游戏工作室<i>100 Stones Interactive</i>的第二款作品，目前正在开发中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即尝试<strong>试玩版</strong>，将游戏加入<strong>愿望清单</strong>，并记得点击<strong>关注按钮</strong>，访问<strong>社区中心</strong>以获取游戏最新动态和更新信息！</p>",
